name: Women's 'Gunner' Jacket (Blood Raiders black)
description: Advertise your stature as the terror of the celestial skies in this sleek, comfortable jacket. A solid crimson pillar rises in front and back to underline your undeniable and unyielding presence, while an extended length of shiny black from wrist to wrist gives you the commanding appearance you deserve. Finally, the logo of the Blood Raiders advertises your proud support for the only faction that matters.
